    {
      "id": "9b257852-8f39-4044-99e4-8a1b45d2ec27",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Fitness tracking is now being applied to Cognitive load. Authors propose weareable educational fitness trackers. Authors use physiological data to predict cognitive load.",
