    {
      "id": "077a426a-50a0-4586-ac33-8ff7b8258fe9",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "A second study shows that it is possible to predict self-reported mental focus. Paper finishes with discussion on how a wearable device could be used in the real world. ",
